definition: not only (this one)/not just (...) but also

sentences.english: It is not just about assuaging your conscience.
sentences.chinese: 這不僅是有關平息你的良心。

sentences.english: But the Dallas-based carrier isn't just looking at Boeing.
sentences.chinese: 但這家總部位於達拉斯的承運商不僅僅只是眷顧波音。

sentences.english: This system encourages not only internal promotions but lateral moves as well.
sentences.chinese: 該系統不僅鼓勵內部升職也支持平職調換。

sentences.english: Not only can walking fish live out of water but they can also travel short distances over land.
sentences.chinese: 鮎魚不僅可以離開水存活，還可以在岸上短間隔移動。

sentences.english: Leo Fender’s guitars weren’t just versatile, they were also durable.
sentences.chinese: 利奧芬達的吉他不僅萬能，而且耐久。

sentences.english: The story speaks of more than thankfulness.
sentences.chinese: 這故事講述的不僅僅是感激之情。

sentences.english: All told, this will not only directly help  families and businesses.
sentences.chinese: 總之，這項計劃不僅僅會直接幫助家庭和企業。

sentences.english: The habitability of Earth depends on a lot more than just orbit location and its mass.
sentences.chinese: 地球的可居住性不僅僅取決於它的位置和雲層。

sentences.english: It is not just foreigners who worry.
sentences.chinese: 擔心這個問題的不僅是外國人。

sentences.english: Tarpaulin, can be seen everywhere in China and is said not only very unique landscape.
sentences.chinese: 篷布，在中國不僅隨處可見而且是道很獨特的風景。

sentences.english: To play Mah-jong well depends on both your skill and luck.
sentences.chinese: 要玩好麻將不僅要靠技術還要靠運氣。

sentences.english: The shortcomings of China’s medical system are hardly limited to cosmetic and plastic surgery.
sentences.chinese: 中國醫療系統的弊病絕不僅僅侷限於美容整形外科。

sentences.english: Leukocyte telomere length (LTL) reflects not only chronologic age but also the burden of disease. We hypothesized that LTL would be decreased in children with OSA.
sentences.chinese: 白細胞端粒長度不僅反映年齡變化而且反映疾病負擔。

sentences.english: Life consists of not only sunshine but also hard times.
sentences.chinese: 生活不僅充滿陽光也會有困難時期。

sentences.english: That series s selling point was not just sex and designer clothes.
sentences.chinese: 這一電視劇的賣點不僅只是性和名牌服裝。

sentences.english: Asimo can walk, climb stairs and recognize voices.
sentences.chinese: 阿西莫不僅會走路，會上樓梯，還會辨認聲音。

definition: regarding/as far as sth is concerned/with regards to
one's conduct/deed/activity/accomplishment/achievement/to act as/as (in the capacity of)/qua/to view as/to look upon (sth as)/to take sth to be
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
and/furthermore/also/together with/(not) at all/simultaneously/to combine/to join/to merge
after all/all in all/when all is said and done/in the final analysis
